What about Tunav?

GPS solutions Leader for already 12 years!

Founded in 2004 by Mr. Anis Kalel, Tunav has since established itself as one of the leading GPS solutions providers.

Thanks to its 12 years of experience and research, Tunav has now a wide range of GPS navigation and tracking solutions, cartographic applications and geo portals

Read more
Chief Executive Officer

Mr. Anis Kallel

Strong values have been at the heart of our company since its inception. These values guide our actions on a daily basis and constitute a common foundation that all partners and collaborators Tunav share and commit to respect

The vocation of Tunav is not to sell a product or service but to be the partner on whom one can count and with whom one wins.

LaTrace®

LaTrace® is a comprehensive GPS / GPRS tracking system that has a wide range of features to manage your entire fleet of vehicles in an easy and efficient way.

This allows you to have a comprehensive and detailed view of the activities of all your vehicles and receive in real time all the information needed for better governance and intelligent management.

Read more
